  "contentHtml": "<h2>Introducing Works in Progress Out Loud</h2>\n<p><span>You can now listen to Works in Progress articles. The mellifluous voice of Stuart Richie, who you may recognize from the podcast </span><a href=\"https://sciencefictionspod.substack.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Science Fictions</a><span>, will be bringing you a new article every week. We’re starting today with </span><em><a href=\"https://worksinprogress.co/issue/two-is-already-too-many/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Two is already too many</a><span>, </span></em><span>a piece from Issue 21 about why South Korean fertility rates are so low, by Phoebe Arslanagic-Little.</span></p>\n<p><span>We’ll be publishing a mix of new articles and pieces from the back catalogue. You can find them on the main Works in Progress podcast feed on </span><a href=\"https://podcasts.apple.com/gb/podcast/two-is-already-too-many-by-phoebe-arslanagic-little/id1819488714?i=1000753651089\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Apple</a><span> and </span><a href=\"https://open.spotify.com/show/3SiNrPYpk4JIzgiv5xGjLT\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Spotify</a><span>, our </span><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=lMjO0CiKGKY\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">YouTube</a><span> channel, and as </span><a href=\"https://www.worksinprogress.news/s/out-loud\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">a new section</a><span> on our Substack.</span></p>\n<h4>Discussion about this episode</h4>\n<img src=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!vCd1!,w_150,h_150,c_fill,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep,g_center/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-video.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fvideo_upload%2Fpost%2F191248220%2Fc0d2b390-4632-466d-b78f-43f1fb07b498%2Ftranscoded-1773752748.png\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">\n<img src=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!WcfC!,w_150,h_150,c_fill,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep,g_center/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-video.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fvideo_upload%2Fpost%2F191242596%2F4a5dcbeb-49fb-492c-950b-45d993aa51d7%2Ftranscoded-1773751205.png\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">\n<img src=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!2p1p!,w_150,h_150,c_fill,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep,g_center/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-video.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fvideo_upload%2Fpost%2F191239405%2F85056331-fbbc-47c7-b235-17eade52eaa6%2Ftranscoded-1773748839.png\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">\n<img src=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!Hxb6!,w_150,h_150,c_fill,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep,g_center/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-video.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fvideo_upload%2Fpost%2F190827688%2F025f80c5-1a56-4ee1-8380-ff36a96989d4%2Ftranscoded-1773414236.png\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">",
